【知乎日报】千万用户的选择，做朋友圈里的新鲜事分享大牛。
        <a href=\"http://daily.zhihu.com?utm_source=rssyanwenzi&utm_campaign=tuijian&utm_medium=rssnormal\" target=\"_blank\">点击下载</a><br>") (dc:creator ((xmlns:dc . "http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/")) "刘博洋") (pubDate nil "Wed, 25 Nov 2015 23:00:00 +0800") (guid nil "http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/astrobaguaology/20367678")) (item nil (title nil "[10X]10个小摩尔") (link nil "http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/archtavern/20365144?utm_campaign=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_source=rss&utm_content=title") (description nil "<img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/5530021cf657992205bb0b59b4364c8a_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image\">收了可观的小费后，酒馆老板小声道：听说上一篇专栏还没解封_(:3 」∠)_ <br><p>摄影狮对它恨之入骨，然而建筑狮却可以化敌为友，利用它做出酷炫的设计。<br></p><p>本期介绍10个小摩尔。<br></p><p>简单的说，摩尔纹是两列频率接近的条纹叠加，在重合的地方得到加强形成的。<br></p><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/04c89e420a446d4d5f86e416aca3e3f8_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"799\" data-rawheight=\"129\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"799\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/04c89e420a446d4d5f86e416aca3e3f8_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/fe0e3c4eafe51c37f62c549d5a0b3630_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"799\" data-rawheight=\"90\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"799\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/fe0e3c4eafe51c37f62c549d5a0b3630_r.jpg\"><p>更详细的解释请看这里：</p><p><a href=\"http://forum.xitek.com/thread-269515-1-1-1.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">摩尔纹的原理与产生条件<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a></p><br><p><b>学校小摩尔</b></p><p>在布里斯班，有一座女子学校的立面设计获奖无数。它的西立面正对高速公路，当汽车经过它时，车内的人可以看到立面呈现出不断变化的效果。它的外层是一系列铜镀铝的百叶，可以抵挡布里斯班的烈日，内层是白墙和上面黑色的条纹。<br></p><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/27f963bf1b3afccf4f6d1193cb321536_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"470\" data-rawheight=\"264\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"470\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/27f963bf1b3afccf4f6d1193cb321536_r.jpg\"><p><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/cb9f68e5e07a5312c982e663b2b0cf77_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"332\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/cb9f68e5e07a5312c982e663b2b0cf77_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/43d2ad73b8f8b15ae16a81ccef87565c_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"501\" data-rawheight=\"402\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"501\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/43d2ad73b8f8b15ae16a81ccef87565c_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/8afde2386c3665efedb635ab749557d6_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"497\" data-rawheight=\"330\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"497\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/8afde2386c3665efedb635ab749557d6_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/c44f26c6e78a2a9b1a4b8fd311c263f7_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1437\" data-rawheight=\"254\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1437\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/c44f26c6e78a2a9b1a4b8fd311c263f7_r.jpg\">可以翻墙看这个视频，绝对亮瞎！</p><p><a href=\"https://vimeo.com/1722855\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">m3 moiré façade model on Vimeo<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a><br></p><br><p><b>UN小摩尔</b></p><p>这个建筑表皮的策略是造成一种视觉假象。立面有两层，表层是直的，内层呈一定角度。在内外层的共同作用下，在平的立面上形成波浪的效果。<br></p><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/fd35a24ceaa92d0177911af4777d0164_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"2400\" data-rawheight=\"1500\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2400\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/fd35a24ceaa92d0177911af4777d0164_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/451f3a81521cf43fe6a9203d9c1bed98_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"2400\" data-rawheight=\"1500\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2400\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/451f3a81521cf43fe6a9203d9c1bed98_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/171938c2f7aa497ea8f75bd3bc8adbbc_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"2400\" data-rawheight=\"1500\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2400\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/171938c2f7aa497ea8f75bd3bc8adbbc_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/b0eb9ec50066347c70c9164732c78863_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"2400\" data-rawheight=\"1500\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2400\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/b0eb9ec50066347c70c9164732c78863_r.jpg\"><p><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/97c9e6bfb84cb13a6f59c58045ca2a5d_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"2400\" data-rawheight=\"1500\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2400\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/97c9e6bfb84cb13a6f59c58045ca2a5d_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/dc3202b74b11f6ef3575682282fdec94_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"2400\" data-rawheight=\"1500\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2400\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/dc3202b74b11f6ef3575682282fdec94_r.jpg\"><b>耶稣小摩尔</b></p><p>最近在做一个教堂。老板让我把耶稣的头像放到外墙上。</p><p>于是我做了这个。</p><p><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/ffbbe811f0f06566fb2c763e596f801b_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"578\" data-rawheight=\"609\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"578\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/ffbbe811f0f06566fb2c763e596f801b_r.jpg\">老板看了说，要低调。。</p><p>于是我又改成了这样。</p><p><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/2d298865073a213a4918b796c8544eae_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"641\" data-rawheight=\"682\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"641\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/2d298865073a213a4918b796c8544eae_r.jpg\">老板看了说，低调。</p><p>然后我又改。找了个黑白图片，用gh改成斜线，最后叠加出来。</p><p>效果就是，当你站在远处的时候，看起来就是一坨普通的墙，当你慢慢靠近，突然就有一张脸浮现出来，吓死你~</p><p><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/783f72ab9185e265699151d2baa0d279_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"940\" data-rawheight=\"317\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"940\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/783f72ab9185e265699151d2baa0d279_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/fe22d90ff244f4a2db8df9e900b64558_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1305\" data-rawheight=\"580\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1305\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/fe22d90ff244f4a2db8df9e900b64558_r.jpg\">老板看了说，WOW!!! It is verging on alchemy!</p><br><p><b>车库小摩尔</b></p><p>在曼哈顿，一栋有40年历史的车库进行了立面改造。立面由两层直径为1 1/4英寸的缆绳组成。<br></p><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/5a5184d026bba7c945a32cbe039c7b39_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"576\" data-rawheight=\"945\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"576\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/5a5184d026bba7c945a32cbe039c7b39_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/c9784562b65836a819527447f4a8c4b3_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"533\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/c9784562b65836a819527447f4a8c4b3_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/fa5cd8196c2cfe6ee5001caa8752121e_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"576\" data-rawheight=\"588\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"576\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/fa5cd8196c2cfe6ee5001caa8752121e_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/1c83169159b2b80fde3d4093f5979921_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"600\" data-rawheight=\"300\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"600\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/1c83169159b2b80fde3d4093f5979921_r.jpg\"><br><p><b>屏风小摩尔</b></p><p>波士顿的Radlab为一栋公寓的大厅设计了两扇屏风。这两扇用桦木板做成的屏风呈曲面，当你与屏风呈垂直角度时，你可以看穿它；当你与它呈一定角度时，你可以看到不断变化的条纹。由此创造了透明与不透明间的对话。<br></p><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/8425ff24d329db040e96d8885428518e_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"550\" data-rawheight=\"401\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"550\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/8425ff24d329db040e96d8885428518e_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/a1131cce2e1fe0705da1a25d6b15635f_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"550\" data-rawheight=\"401\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"550\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/a1131cce2e1fe0705da1a25d6b15635f_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/a1a520b2f645172a2e3b7eb9deca59e7_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"800\" data-rawheight=\"584\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"800\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/a1a520b2f645172a2e3b7eb9deca59e7_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/ab6fb78259fcb29a359d7579b2352f5a_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"800\" data-rawheight=\"533\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"800\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/ab6fb78259fcb29a359d7579b2352f5a_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/8d8c567abe578523ca72080c5790f658_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"900\" data-rawheight=\"552\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"900\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/8d8c567abe578523ca72080c5790f658_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/de3e09bfcd017c42c12779fd44998491_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"900\" data-rawheight=\"847\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"900\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/de3e09bfcd017c42c12779fd44998491_r.jpg\"><br><p><b>体育馆小摩尔</b></p><p>新加坡的国家体育馆。<br></p><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/a3b2cdf7b36cceb4a157c32252d85e32_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"818\" data-rawheight=\"499\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"818\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/a3b2cdf7b36cceb4a157c32252d85e32_r.jpg\"><br><p><b>商场小摩尔</b></p><p>UN给台湾设计的商场。第一眼你一定以为自己的屏幕坏掉了。</p><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/cb02ce9baabc669b87228648557d991e_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"450\" data-rawheight=\"320\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"450\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/cb02ce9baabc669b87228648557d991e_r.jpg\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/96cf1968e65954c7673a0e1fd29bc278_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"400\" data-rawheight=\"400\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"400\"><br><br><p>（完）</p><br><br><p><b>[10X]系列文章链接：</b><br></p><br><p><a href=\"http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/archtavern/19991961\" class=\"internal\">[10X]10个小酒店</a></p><p><a href=\"http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/archtavern/20002333\" class=\"internal\">[10X]10个小墓碑</a></p><p><a href=\"http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/archtavern/20010207\" class=\"internal\">[10X]10个小教堂</a></p><p><a href=\"http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/archtavern/20019708\" class=\"internal\">[10X]10个小车库</a><